/** @format */

import React, { Fragment } from "react";
import { Grid, Card, CardContent, Typography } from "@mui/material";

const MatterCards = () => {
  return (
    <Fragment>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item>
          <Card sx={{ minWidth: 200 }}>
            <Grid container>
              <CardContent>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  Urgent
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6}>
                  0
                </Grid>
              </CardContent>
            </Grid>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item item>
          <Card sx={{ minWidth: 160 }}>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography
                sx={{ fontSize: 12 }}
                color="text.secondary"
                gutterBottom
              >
                Concern
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">
                0
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
          <Card sx={{ minWidth: 160 }}>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography
                sx={{ fontSize: 12 }}
                color="text.secondary"
                gutterBottom
              >
                Start
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">
                0
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
          <Card sx={{ minWidth: 160 }}>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography
                sx={{ fontSize: 12 }}
                color="text.secondary"
                gutterBottom
              >
                New
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">
                0
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Fragment>
  );
};

export default MatterCards;
